\[\bm{C}_{k}^{\bm{y}|k}=\bm{A}\bm{D}\text{diag}(\bm{\gamma}_{k})\bm{D}^{\mathsf{ T}}\bm{A}^{\mathsf{T}}+\sigma^{2}\,\bm{\mathrm{I}}\,.\] (17)

